# Build context is the repo root (docker-compose `context: .`).
# Without this, Docker tars .venv, .git, backups → huge context, pipe errors, slow builds.

.venv
venv
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

__pycache__
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.Python
*.so
.pytest_cache
.mypy_cache
.ruff_cache
.coverage
htmlcov

.git
.gitignore
.idea
.vscode
.cursor
.claude

node_modules
npm-debug.log*

backups
archived*
*.backup*
*backup*
**/web-dashboard-service.backup.*

*.md
!README.md

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
terminals

# Large / irrelevant trees
**/archived_emergency_scripts*
**/final_cleanup_archive*
